1
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:05,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Gregory!</font>

2
00:00:10,500 --> 00:00:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Damn it, we're done for at this rate...</font>

3
00:00:13,420 --> 00:00:16,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There's gotta be something I can do!</font>

4
00:00:17,130 --> 00:00:22,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Run away.
Run away.</font>

5
00:00:17,130 --> 00:00:20,540
<font size="53" color="#ff0000"><b>{\an7} r u n</b></font>

6
00:00:20,540 --> 00:00:23,130
<font size="53" color="#ff0000"><b>{\an7}R U N</b></font>

7
00:00:23,130 --> 00:00:29,630
<font size="46" color="#ff0000"><b>{\an7}Divine Voice</b></font>

8
00:00:23,130 --> 00:00:29,630
<font size="46" color="#ff0000"><b>{\an7}Lv 4</b></font>

9
00:00:24,250 --> 00:00:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Divine Voice skill has gone
from level three to level four.</font>

10
00:00:29,630 --> 00:00:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You can now access the
simplified simulator rendered by Laplace.</font>

11
00:00:29,630 --> 00:00:35,080
<font size="53" color="#ff0000"><b>{\an7}Laplace</b></font>

12
00:00:29,630 --> 00:00:35,080
<font size="53" color="#ff0000"><b>{\an7}Simplified</b></font>

13
00:00:29,630 --> 00:00:35,080
<font size="53" color="#ff0000"><b>{\an7}Simulator</b></font>

14
00:00:35,290 --> 00:00:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What's the big idea?</font>

15
00:00:37,330 --> 00:00:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whaddaya mean
the Divine Voice leveled up?!</font>

16
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:41,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But I imagine...</font>

17
00:00:41,790 --> 00:00:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">you will not run
no matter how much I warn you.</font>

18
00:00:46,250 --> 00:00:49,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You were an exception to the rule,
in so many ways.</font>

19
00:00:49,330 --> 00:00:52,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's unfortunate
this is where we must part.</font>

20
00:00:52,210 --> 00:00:57,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So you leveled up
just to tell me this crap?!</font>

21
00:00:57,880 --> 00:01:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I never got tired of watching you.</font>

22
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Rest peacefully now.</font>

23
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:07,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm so sick of your condescending babble!</font>

24
00:01:07,380 --> 00:01:09,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Just who the hell are you?!</font>

25
00:01:09,540 --> 00:01:14,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Divine Voice cannot provide
explanations of that nature at level four.</font>

26
00:01:16,380 --> 00:01:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Screw that noise!</font>

27
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:21,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm gonna prove you wrong!</font>

28
00:01:21,170 --> 00:01:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I still have my last resort...</font>

29
00:01:26,130 --> 00:01:27,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Evolution.</font>

30
00:01:27,880 --> 00:01:30,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But it'll change how I look,</font>

31
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:35,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">which means Myria and the black lizard
may not recognize me anymore.</font>

32
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There are four different evolutions
I can choose from now.</font>

33
00:01:41,750 --> 00:01:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Which one should I choose? Think!</font>

34
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Jormungand.</font>

35
00:01:46,790 --> 00:01:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I might stand a chance at winning
if I pick that,</font>

36
00:01:49,210 --> 00:01:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">but its deadly poison
is seriously bad news!</font>

37
00:01:51,540 --> 00:01:52,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Rolling Dragon!</font>

38
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:54,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It specializes in the Roll skill, right?</font>

39
00:01:54,790 --> 00:01:56,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is that actually powerful?!</font>

40
00:01:56,630 --> 00:01:58,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Dark Drago-human!</font>

41
00:01:58,670 --> 00:02:00,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But are demi-humans good in battle?</font>

42
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I have no idea what to expect!</font>

43
00:02:03,210 --> 00:02:05,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Little Arc Dragon!</font>

44
00:02:05,130 --> 00:02:07,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Can white magic be used to attack?</font>

45
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:10,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is it enough to beat that bastard?!</font>

46
00:02:11,290 --> 00:02:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Which one?</font>

47
00:02:12,540 --> 00:02:13,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What should I choose?!</font>

48
00:02:14,580 --> 00:02:17,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Which one is most likely to win?!</font>

49
00:02:22,170 --> 00:02:23,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What was that just now?</font>

50
00:02:23,710 --> 00:02:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's like all my MP got taken from me...</font>

51
00:02:26,670 --> 00:02:30,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You have received the title
"Laplace Authority Interference."</font>

52
00:02:31,670 --> 00:02:45,290
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Little Arc Dragon</b></font>

53
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:36,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If you evolve into Little Arc Dragon,
your odds of winning are 4%.</font>

54
00:02:36,830 --> 00:02:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There is a less than 1% chance
of you saving all your injured allies.</font>

55
00:02:41,670 --> 00:02:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The hell does that mean?</font>

56
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:45,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Are you telling me I can't win
even if I evolve?!</font>

57
00:02:46,130 --> 00:02:58,080
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Jormungand</b></font>

58
00:02:47,670 --> 00:02:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If you evolve into Jormungand, your odds
of ending the battle in a draw are 98%.</font>

59
00:02:53,580 --> 00:02:57,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There is a 94% chance
the village is totally destroyed.</font>

60
00:02:58,420 --> 00:03:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What's the point
if I can't protect the village?!</font>

61
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:05,040
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Rolling Dragon</b></font>

62
00:03:01,710 --> 00:03:06,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If you evolve into Rolling Dragon,
you have less than a 1% chance of victory.</font>

63
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:10,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Your odds of a successful escape
are over 99%.</font>

64
00:03:10,670 --> 00:03:12,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So you're still telling me
to run away, then?!</font>

65
00:03:17,710 --> 00:03:19,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I don't get it.</font>

66
00:03:19,170 --> 00:03:23,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Why are you giving me
all these predictions?!</font>

67
00:03:23,330 --> 00:03:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You stupid voice!</font>

68
00:03:43,750 --> 00:03:50,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Tsuyoku nare itami yo yuuki ni nare</font>

69
00:03:57,630 --> 00:04:01,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Nani ga umaretan darou</font>

70
00:04:01,630 --> 00:04:06,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Te o nobashi fureta sekai wa</font>

71
00:04:06,830 --> 00:04:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kanashikute moroi kagayaki</font>

72
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Dakara koso no more painess</font>

73
00:04:21,130 --> 00:04:25,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kono basho de mirai no kodou</font>

74
00:04:26,210 --> 00:04:29,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kanjitara mou tomerarenai</font>

75
00:04:29,460 --> 00:04:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Hikari oikakete</font>

76
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:34,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Gliding Claw</font>

77
00:04:34,210 --> 00:04:38,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Dare ka no koto mamoritakunatta</font>

78
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:43,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Sou... dakara makenai makerarenai yo</font>

79
00:04:43,330 --> 00:04:44,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Gliding Claw</font>

80
00:04:44,580 --> 00:04:51,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Wakatta no wa chiisana jibun ga kawareru koto da to</font>

81
00:04:51,830 --> 00:04:58,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Tsuyoku nare itami yo yuuki ni nare</font>

82
00:05:10,130 --> 00:05:13,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I heard a loud noise
coming from the village.</font>

83
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's hurry.</font>

84
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:25,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Rock Dragon is going berserk.</font>

85
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:28,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Have all the villagers evacuated?</font>

86
00:05:28,130 --> 00:05:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No, quite a few of them
haven't shown up yet.</font>

87
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:32,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, Jean!</font>

88
00:05:39,210 --> 00:05:40,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Where's Gregory?</font>

89
00:05:40,710 --> 00:05:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">In the center of town.</font>

90
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:45,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He and a couple others said
they were going to stop the Rock Dragon.</font>

91
00:05:45,290 --> 00:05:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm heading over there too.</font>

92
00:05:47,290 --> 00:05:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Myria, you provide aid
for the villagers here!</font>

93
00:05:49,750 --> 00:05:52,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No.
I've already helped everyone I can here.</font>

94
00:05:52,790 --> 00:05:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm going with you.</font>

95
00:05:54,670 --> 00:05:55,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But...</font>

96
00:05:56,250 --> 00:05:59,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm sure there are
plenty of injured people over that way.</font>

97
00:06:01,380 --> 00:06:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All right. Come with me.</font>

98
00:06:09,170 --> 00:06:10,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Which one should I choose?</font>

99
00:06:10,290 --> 00:06:12,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I gotta be quick
or this will just get worse!</font>

100
00:06:12,580 --> 00:06:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If I help Gregory first,
evolve into the Little Arc Dragon,</font>

101
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and use recovery magic...</font>

102
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:24,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If you evolve into Little Arc Dragon,
your odds of winning are 4%.</font>

103
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:24,960
<font size="46" color="#ff8080"><b>{\an7}Odds of Winning 4%</b></font>

104
00:06:25,580 --> 00:06:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There is a less than 1% chance
of you saving all your injured allies.</font>

105
00:06:25,580 --> 00:06:30,330
<font size="46" color="#ff8080"><b>{\an7}Saving Injured 1%</b></font>

106
00:06:30,330 --> 00:06:31,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Shut up!</font>

107
00:06:31,540 --> 00:06:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You really think anyone believes
whatever stupid crap you say?!</font>

108
00:06:40,670 --> 00:06:42,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Gregory, are you okay?!</font>

109
00:06:46,290 --> 00:06:48,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He's bleeding out!</font>

110
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Just hold on.</font>

111
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:51,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll evolve into a Little Arc Dragon
and heal you.</font>

112
00:06:55,790 --> 00:06:58,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't worry about me.</font>

113
00:06:59,080 --> 00:07:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh? What do you mean?!</font>

114
00:07:02,210 --> 00:07:08,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What reason could a Plague Dragon
like you have to help humans?</font>

115
00:07:09,460 --> 00:07:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I have absolutely no clue.</font>

116
00:07:11,750 --> 00:07:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It makes no sense,
but there is one thing I'm convinced of...</font>

117
00:07:16,130 --> 00:07:17,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's fine, stop talking!</font>

118
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:20,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll heal you very soon!</font>

119
00:07:21,250 --> 00:07:22,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You...</font>

120
00:07:22,580 --> 00:07:27,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">aren't using your true power, are you?</font>

121
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hey... do me a favor.</font>

122
00:07:33,750 --> 00:07:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Eat me.</font>

123
00:07:37,710 --> 00:07:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're a Plague Dragon, right?</font>

124
00:07:40,750 --> 00:07:45,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You eat people,
and then get stronger, right?</font>

125
00:07:45,460 --> 00:07:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No, no, no, never!</font>

126
00:07:47,420 --> 00:07:49,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm not that extreme of a monster!</font>

127
00:07:49,750 --> 00:07:53,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I don't eat people!
And I don't power up like that!</font>

128
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:55,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The only way I get stronger
is through evolution!</font>

129
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:58,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wait...</font>

130
00:07:58,170 --> 00:08:00,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My evolution tree...</font>

131
00:08:00,630 --> 00:08:02,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Young Plague Dragon.</font>

132
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:04,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The first stage of an Evil Dragon
that spreads disaster.</font>

133
00:08:04,250 --> 00:08:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">However, it has not strayed too far from
the righteous path, and may yet backtrack.</font>

134
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:12,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You have received the title
"Itty-Bitty Hero" level one.</font>

135
00:08:12,330 --> 00:08:13,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A light-type!</font>

136
00:08:13,790 --> 00:08:16,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hard to believe a Plague Dragon
can evolve into something so righteous!</font>

137
00:08:17,170 --> 00:08:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You have received the title "Wrongdoer."</font>

138
00:08:20,130 --> 00:08:24,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But like, why is there no Plague Dragon
evolution even though I'm a Plague Dragon?</font>

139
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No Plague Dragon...
No Plague Dragon...</font>

140
00:08:30,960 --> 00:08:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There's no... Plague Dragon.</font>

141
00:08:37,330 --> 00:08:40,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Even though you helped Myria,</font>

142
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:44,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I stabbed you with my spear,</font>

143
00:08:44,580 --> 00:08:50,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and you're still fighting the Rock Dragon
to help us humans.</font>

144
00:08:51,290 --> 00:08:57,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I wanted the humans to accept me,
as the hero who saved their village!</font>

145
00:08:57,790 --> 00:09:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're really not at all
how a monster should be.</font>

146
00:09:03,250 --> 00:09:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But...</font>

147
00:09:05,710 --> 00:09:09,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">if that's the reason
you can't beat the Rock Dragon, then...</font>

148
00:09:13,420 --> 00:09:16,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Gregory, what are you...</font>

149
00:09:20,250 --> 00:09:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The village...</font>

150
00:09:23,330 --> 00:09:26,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Protect the village, Illusia...</font>

151
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:56,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Because you have maxed out your level,
you cannot gain experience points.</font>

152
00:09:56,500 --> 00:10:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Wrongdoer title
has gone from level four to level five</font>

153
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Calamity title
has gone from level one to level three,</font>

154
00:10:04,750 --> 00:10:08,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and the Dastardly King title
has gone from level one to level two.</font>

155
00:10:09,130 --> 00:10:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That was a major level up.</font>

156
00:10:12,630 --> 00:10:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There really is
no turning back for me now.</font>

157
00:10:15,500 --> 00:10:17,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Would you like to view the evolution tree?</font>

158
00:10:17,830 --> 00:10:19,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Show me right now.</font>

159
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Plague Dragon, Rank B-.</font>

160
00:10:23,420 --> 00:10:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">An evil dragon that brings disaster
wherever it roams.</font>

161
00:10:25,670 --> 00:10:27,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It has destroyed many human villages.</font>

162
00:10:28,460 --> 00:10:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It bathes itself in a sea of blood,</font>

163
00:10:30,420 --> 00:10:32,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and sleeps atop
the resulting mountain of corpses.</font>

164
00:10:30,420 --> 00:10:36,670
<font size="34"><b>{\an7}Plague Dragon</b></font>

165
00:10:33,290 --> 00:10:36,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It is one of the three
great Calamity monsters.</font>

166
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I will...</font>

167
00:10:38,540 --> 00:10:41,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">evolve into a Plague Dragon!</font>

168
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:09,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't worry.</font>

169
00:11:09,460 --> 00:11:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I will make sure to protect the village!</font>

170
00:11:12,460 --> 00:11:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">With the power
that your sacrifice gave me!</font>

171
00:11:22,170 --> 00:11:25,420
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Status: Enraged (Major)</b></font>

172
00:11:25,420 --> 00:11:28,920
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Attack:</b></font>

173
00:11:25,420 --> 00:11:28,920
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Defense:</b></font>

174
00:11:25,420 --> 00:11:28,920
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Magic:</b></font>

175
00:11:25,420 --> 00:11:28,920
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Agility:</b></font>

176
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Crap, you are way too heavy!</font>

177
00:11:41,580 --> 00:11:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It figures that I can't beat this guy
in a shoving match.</font>

178
00:11:44,710 --> 00:11:46,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But...</font>

179
00:11:50,750 --> 00:11:51,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Take this!</font>

180
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeah, that's some thick skin!</font>

181
00:11:54,540 --> 00:11:55,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But I'm not done!</font>

182
00:11:59,580 --> 00:12:01,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay, the stage is set.</font>

183
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:05,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is where...</font>

184
00:12:07,170 --> 00:12:09,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I whoop you!</font>

185
00:12:10,040 --> 00:12:14,000
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}I Evolved Into an Evil Dragon</b></font>

186
00:12:17,750 --> 00:12:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Illusia!</font>

187
00:12:19,290 --> 00:12:20,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mr. Gregory!</font>

188
00:12:21,790 --> 00:12:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Where'd the Rock Dragon go?</font>

189
00:12:28,540 --> 00:12:30,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aurus, you're okay?!</font>

190
00:12:30,830 --> 00:12:33,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Where are the others?
What's happened to Gregory?</font>

191
00:12:43,330 --> 00:12:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Gregory...</font>

192
00:12:44,710 --> 00:12:46,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What in the world happened?</font>

193
00:12:46,670 --> 00:12:48,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It was the black dragon!</font>

194
00:12:48,250 --> 00:12:50,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It killed Gregory!</font>

195
00:12:50,380 --> 00:12:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Black dragon?</font>

196
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:54,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You mean the Plague Dragon
Myria brought here?!</font>

197
00:12:55,250 --> 00:12:56,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He couldn't have...</font>

198
00:12:56,330 --> 00:12:57,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I saw it with my own eyes!</font>

199
00:12:57,920 --> 00:13:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The black dragon cut Gregory's head off!</font>

200
00:13:01,380 --> 00:13:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then it suddenly got bigger...</font>

201
00:13:04,250 --> 00:13:05,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It grew?</font>

202
00:13:05,750 --> 00:13:07,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You mean it evolved?!</font>

203
00:13:07,830 --> 00:13:09,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I-I don't know.</font>

204
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:12,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It moved east
while fighting the Rock Dragon.</font>

205
00:13:12,460 --> 00:13:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Damn those nasty monsters!</font>

206
00:13:15,460 --> 00:13:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Illusia killed Mr. Gregory?</font>

207
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It can't... It can't be true!</font>

208
00:13:21,380 --> 00:13:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Calm down, Myria.</font>

209
00:13:23,460 --> 00:13:26,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We have more important things
to do right now.</font>

210
00:13:30,830 --> 00:13:31,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Come on.</font>

211
00:13:31,830 --> 00:13:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We need to hurry and treat the injured.</font>

212
00:13:33,920 --> 00:13:34,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">R-right!</font>

213
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aurus, get a move on!</font>

214
00:13:36,330 --> 00:13:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay!</font>

215
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A Rock Dragon and a Plague Dragon, huh?</font>

216
00:13:42,790 --> 00:13:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The village is doomed
if they come back here.</font>

217
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Using Tremor again?</font>

218
00:13:55,830 --> 00:13:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is that all you've got?!</font>

219
00:14:00,460 --> 00:14:02,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's my turn now!</font>

220
00:14:00,630 --> 00:14:02,670
<font size="53" color="#f9c7fd"><b>{\an7}Whirlwind Slash</b></font>

221
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whirlwind Slash!</font>

222
00:14:10,170 --> 00:14:13,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So this is my newly gained skill,
Whirlwind Slash, huh?</font>

223
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How useful.</font>

224
00:14:14,250 --> 00:14:15,000
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Bellow</b></font>

225
00:14:14,250 --> 00:14:15,000
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Meteorite</b></font>

226
00:14:14,250 --> 00:14:15,000
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Nutcracker</b></font>

227
00:14:14,250 --> 00:14:15,000
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Human Transformation</b></font>

228
00:14:14,250 --> 00:14:15,000
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Whirlwind Smash</b></font>

229
00:14:14,250 --> 00:14:15,000
<font size="40"><b>{\an7}Neckbreaker</b></font>

230
00:14:15,460 --> 00:14:17,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've got one called Neckbreaker too.</font>

231
00:14:17,710 --> 00:14:19,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bet that hits hard.</font>

232
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That was close!</font>

233
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'd have been cooked
if that attack hit me!</font>

234
00:14:27,290 --> 00:14:30,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">None of the hits I landed
made a good dent in its HP.</font>

235
00:14:30,040 --> 00:14:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's sturdy as hell.</font>

236
00:14:33,130 --> 00:14:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Doesn't it have a weak spot somewhere?!</font>

237
00:14:36,380 --> 00:14:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Divine Voice cannot provide
explanations of that nature at level four.</font>

238
00:14:41,630 --> 00:14:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yep, I knew you'd say that!</font>

239
00:14:43,670 --> 00:14:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Considering its body is hard as rock,
maybe its weak spot is... the head!</font>

240
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There's nothing I can do but try!</font>

241
00:14:50,460 --> 00:14:52,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Dragon Punch!</font>

242
00:14:57,250 --> 00:14:58,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Onto the next one!</font>

243
00:14:58,460 --> 00:15:00,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Dragon Tail!</font>

244
00:15:01,420 --> 00:15:02,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Try this on for size!</font>

245
00:15:05,830 --> 00:15:08,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hell yeah! I crushed its eyes!</font>

246
00:15:12,210 --> 00:15:14,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This should be easy pickings
if it can't see.</font>

247
00:15:14,250 --> 00:15:16,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can just beat it into submission now!</font>

248
00:15:18,170 --> 00:15:19,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wait, not that way!</font>

249
00:15:22,630 --> 00:15:25,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're not going any further!</font>

250
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:31,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay.</font>

251
00:15:31,580 --> 00:15:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aurus, take those who can move
and evacuate them west of the village.</font>

252
00:15:35,540 --> 00:15:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You got it!</font>

253
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:40,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Myria, we're going to search
around here...</font>

254
00:15:41,580 --> 00:15:42,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Myria?</font>

255
00:15:44,420 --> 00:15:46,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She better not have gone after it!</font>

256
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:08,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Stop!</font>

257
00:16:19,580 --> 00:16:21,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Dragon Scale Powder!</font>

258
00:16:22,170 --> 00:16:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is my poison working on it?!</font>

259
00:16:25,630 --> 00:16:26,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Its neck...</font>

260
00:16:26,920 --> 00:16:30,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You know, the neck
seems slimmer than the rest of it.</font>

261
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:32,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Did I just find its weak spot?</font>

262
00:16:35,130 --> 00:16:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's working!</font>

263
00:16:36,130 --> 00:16:38,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't stop! I gotta pummel it!</font>

264
00:16:41,830 --> 00:16:43,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Almost there!</font>

265
00:16:43,040 --> 00:16:44,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll snap the damn thing!</font>

266
00:16:43,540 --> 00:16:44,750
<font size="53" color="#c4ffff"><b>{\an7}Neckbreaker</b></font>

267
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There it is!</font>

268
00:16:48,040 --> 00:16:49,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Take this!</font>

269
00:16:49,830 --> 00:16:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Neckbreaker!</font>

270
00:17:04,290 --> 00:17:07,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You have received 384 experience points.</font>

271
00:17:09,420 --> 00:17:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Due to the effect
of the "Walking Egg" title,</font>

272
00:17:12,420 --> 00:17:16,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">you have earned an additional
384 experience points.</font>

273
00:17:16,580 --> 00:17:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Plague Dragon
has gone from level 1 to level 19.</font>

274
00:17:22,290 --> 00:17:23,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All right.</font>

275
00:17:24,380 --> 00:17:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I beat it.</font>

276
00:17:29,040 --> 00:17:31,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Illusia?</font>

277
00:17:35,330 --> 00:17:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Myria!</font>

278
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:39,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You are... Illusia, right?</font>

279
00:17:40,170 --> 00:17:42,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You still recognize me?</font>

280
00:17:45,330 --> 00:17:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You beat the Rock Dragon for us, huh?</font>

281
00:17:48,630 --> 00:17:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And you've gotten so big...</font>

282
00:17:50,960 --> 00:17:53,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Did you evolve again?</font>

283
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Evolve?</font>

284
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:57,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, right.</font>

285
00:17:57,460 --> 00:18:00,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I killed Gregory
and turned into this monstrosity...</font>

286
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:01,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Light Sphere!</font>

287
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:04,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Myria, get away from it!</font>

288
00:18:05,080 --> 00:18:06,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What the?!</font>

289
00:18:06,710 --> 00:18:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There's no time to waste, run away!</font>

290
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Please stop, Miss Marielle!</font>

291
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:12,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Myria?!</font>

292
00:18:12,210 --> 00:18:13,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What are you doing?!</font>

293
00:18:13,710 --> 00:18:14,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Miss Marielle!</font>

294
00:18:14,960 --> 00:18:18,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is Illusia,
the dragon I told you about!</font>

295
00:18:18,040 --> 00:18:20,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He's bigger now,
but I'm positive this is him!</font>

296
00:18:20,710 --> 00:18:23,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Gregory was killed by this monster!</font>

297
00:18:27,330 --> 00:18:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Really, Illusia?</font>

298
00:18:37,580 --> 00:18:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Get away from it!</font>

299
00:18:39,830 --> 00:18:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There must be some misunderstanding!</font>

300
00:18:41,630 --> 00:18:43,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Illusia would not do that!</font>

301
00:18:44,960 --> 00:18:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Myria...</font>

302
00:18:46,330 --> 00:18:48,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You believe in me?</font>

303
00:18:53,420 --> 00:18:56,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh yeah, the Dragon Scale Powder!</font>

304
00:18:56,170 --> 00:18:58,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Miss Marielle, I...</font>

305
00:19:00,580 --> 00:19:06,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've turned into a monstrosity
who can't be near her anymore...</font>

306
00:19:06,750 --> 00:19:07,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Myria!</font>

307
00:19:13,380 --> 00:19:14,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Light Sphere!</font>

308
00:19:21,040 --> 00:19:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You must've been hit by
the Plague Dragon's poison.</font>

309
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:26,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No...</font>

310
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:29,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No... Illusia...</font>

311
00:19:30,380 --> 00:19:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Farewell, Myria.</font>

312
00:19:46,630 --> 00:19:49,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So awesome! I'm built like a tank now!</font>

313
00:19:49,250 --> 00:19:51,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I bet I can kick so much ass!</font>

314
00:19:56,830 --> 00:19:59,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My whole body feels stiff.</font>

315
00:19:59,130 --> 00:20:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aren't I supposed to have
automatic recovery?</font>

316
00:20:09,460 --> 00:20:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You know, I never really cared
about flowers until today...</font>

317
00:20:15,710 --> 00:20:19,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Illusia, Value D+.</font>

318
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:23,380
<font size="53"><b>{\an7}Illusia</b></font>

319
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's... my name.</font>

320
00:20:24,290 --> 00:20:27,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A beautiful red and white flower.</font>

321
00:20:27,710 --> 00:20:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It is said this flower only blooms
where monsters live.</font>

322
00:20:33,080 --> 00:20:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">For that reason,
these flowers are difficult to gather,</font>

323
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and they make excellent gifts.</font>

324
00:20:40,210 --> 00:20:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">In flower language,
it symbolizes courage, bravery,</font>

325
00:20:44,710 --> 00:20:46,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and heroism.</font>

326
00:20:47,080 --> 00:20:48,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're a hero.</font>

327
00:20:50,170 --> 00:20:52,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How about... Illusia?</font>

328
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:55,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's the name of a flower I like.</font>

329
00:21:04,040 --> 00:21:05,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Erase it!</font>

330
00:21:05,290 --> 00:21:07,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Get rid of this name!</font>

331
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:12,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Once your name is confirmed,
it cannot be changed.</font>

332
00:21:12,580 --> 00:21:15,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bravery? A hero?!</font>

333
00:21:15,710 --> 00:21:18,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You really think I can use this name?!</font>

334
00:21:18,790 --> 00:21:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Delete it! Get rid of it this instant!</font>

335
00:21:21,750 --> 00:21:26,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Once your name is confirmed,
it cannot be changed.</font>

336
00:21:29,920 --> 00:21:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm an idiot.</font>

337
00:21:31,710 --> 00:21:34,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A huge idiot!</font>

338
00:21:36,250 --> 00:21:40,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What was it I wanted to become?</font>

339
00:21:41,080 --> 00:21:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What did I want to do?</font>

340
00:21:45,580 --> 00:21:49,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Why was I even brought to this world?</font>

341
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:53,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What's that sound?</font>

342
00:21:54,670 --> 00:21:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ah, whatever, I don't care anymore...</font>

343
00:22:00,670 --> 00:22:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Can you tell me? Shinjita kotoba</font>

344
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Never ending kawareru bokura</font>

345
00:22:07,250 --> 00:22:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Always remember yakusoku nakutashita page</font>

346
00:22:10,960 --> 00:22:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Owaranai monogatari o</font>

347
00:22:13,420 --> 00:22:17,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Don't let nobody bring you down</font>

348
00:22:19,920 --> 00:22:24,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Tokihanate break of dawn</font>

349
00:22:27,170 --> 00:22:30,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kirei na mama no omoide nara</font>

350
00:22:30,630 --> 00:22:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Oitakita through the rain</font>

351
00:22:33,580 --> 00:22:37,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Tesaguri demo mae ni susumu emotion</font>

352
00:22:37,210 --> 00:22:39,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Tsune ni mune ni daite</font>

353
00:22:40,210 --> 00:22:41,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Atomodori wa nashi</font>

354
00:22:41,830 --> 00:22:43,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kokoro ni oshita rakuin</font>

355
00:22:43,460 --> 00:22:45,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Shoki shoudou no mama ni</font>

356
00:22:45,130 --> 00:22:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Attouteki na made ni</font>

357
00:22:46,790 --> 00:22:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Hisometa ketsui hyoumei wa</font>

358
00:22:48,290 --> 00:22:49,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Kakumei no makuake sa</font>

359
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Hajimeyou ka 3, 2, 1 GO!!</font>

360
00:22:52,250 --> 00:22:55,500
